03:19.366 --> 03:21.242
don't track mud

03:19.366 --> 03:21.242
into this house?!

03:21.284 --> 03:22.243
We'll clean it up.

03:22.285 --> 03:23.244
That's not good enough!

03:23.286 --> 03:24.454
You're grounded

03:23.286 --> 03:24.454
for a week!

03:24.496 --> 03:25.873
What?!

03:24.496 --> 03:25.873
You can't do that.

03:25.914 --> 03:27.248
It's just some

03:25.914 --> 03:27.248
stupid footprints.

03:27.290 --> 03:28.750
You want to be

03:27.290 --> 03:28.750
grounded for two weeks?

03:28.792 --> 03:29.668
Dad?

03:29.710 --> 03:30.878
