03:37.134 --> 03:38.719
be grounded.

03:38.760 --> 03:41.221
Go to your room. Now!

03:42.931 --> 03:44.850
What is her problem?

03:44.892 --> 03:46.560
Mom and Dad--

03:44.892 --> 03:46.560
their lives are so boring

03:46.601 --> 03:49.104
they have to invent

03:46.601 --> 03:49.104
stuff to be upset about.

03:52.983 --> 03:56.653
Are you the biggest idiot

03:52.983 --> 03:56.653
to ever walk this Earth?

03:56.695 --> 03:58.155
Good morning.

03:58.197 --> 04:00.323
What'd I tell you

03:58.197 --> 04:00.323
to do, jackass?

04:00.365 --> 04:02.910
To paint the kitchen.

04:00.365 --> 04:02.910
Which I'm doing.

04:02.951 --> 04:05.537
What kind of a moron

04:02.951 --> 04:05.537
paints a kitchen white?

04:05.579 --> 04:07.539
You want to see

04:05.579 --> 04:07.539
