04:07.581 --> 04:09.290
What do they teach you

04:07.581 --> 04:09.290
in college, anyway?

04:09.332 --> 04:12.169
For your information,

04:09.332 --> 04:12.169
I'm a high school dropout.

04:12.211 --> 04:14.295
And I used the paint

04:12.211 --> 04:14.295
that you set out for me.

04:14.337 --> 04:15.463
I moved that paint

04:15.505 --> 04:16.965
so you could get

04:15.505 --> 04:16.965
to the green, idiot.

04:17.007 --> 04:18.341
Now, you're going

04:17.007 --> 04:18.341
to do this over.

04:18.383 --> 04:20.510
I don't care if you're

04:18.383 --> 04:20.510
here all night doing it.

04:20.552 --> 04:22.303
What?!

04:20.552 --> 04:22.303
That paint you wasted

04:22.345 --> 04:24.973
