I said...

04:37.736 --> 04:41.322
maybe I should just paint it

04:37.736 --> 04:41.322
the same color as your dye job,

04:41.364 --> 04:43.700
you sagging, leathery,

04:41.364 --> 04:43.700
hatchet-faced,

04:43.742 --> 04:45.744
