04:56.296 --> 04:57.547
Francis, what

04:56.296 --> 04:57.547
are you doing?

04:57.589 --> 04:58.840
You can't challenge

04:57.589 --> 04:58.840
Lavernia to a fight.

04:58.882 --> 05:00.175
I didn't

04:58.882 --> 05:00.175
challenge anybody.

