Sunday, 2:00--

05:06.556 --> 05:09.851
your ass, my foot.

05:09.893 --> 05:11.228
This is insane.

05:11.270 --> 05:12.353
There's no way

05:11.270 --> 05:12.353
I'm going to fight a woman.

05:12.395 --> 05:14.815
If I don't mind,

05:12.395 --> 05:14.815
