06:49.368 --> 06:51.245
Yeah, and her sister Gina's

06:49.368 --> 06:51.245
bringing all their friends

06:51.286 --> 06:52.329
from Catholic school.

06:52.371 --> 06:53.330
I love those girls.

06:53.372 --> 06:54.373
