07:00.503 --> 07:04.465
Reese, if I show you a way

07:00.503 --> 07:04.465
we can go to the party,

07:04.507 --> 07:07.135
do you promise never

07:04.507 --> 07:07.135
to let anyone find out,

07:07.177 --> 07:08.845
even though

07:07.177 --> 07:08.845
you're an idiot?

07:08.887 --> 07:09.846
I swear.

07:09.888 --> 07:11.514
Okay.

07:13.516 --> 07:16.353
I was saving this

07:13.516 --> 07:16.353
