07:28.907 --> 07:32.160
Reese, tomorrow night, after

07:28.907 --> 07:32.160
everyone's gone to bed,

07:32.202 --> 07:33.494
we take out the floorboard

07:33.536 --> 07:35.496
and sneak outside

07:33.536 --> 07:35.496
through the crawl space.

07:35.538 --> 07:39.167
Wow. Tunneling out

07:35.538 --> 07:39.167
of our own room.

07:39.209 --> 07:41.378
She can't

07:39.209 --> 07:41.378
lock us in anymore.

07:41.420 --> 07:42.670
Mom's powerless.

07:42.712 --> 07:45.006
Yeah, now she's just

07:42.712 --> 07:45.006
a crazy old lady

07:45.048 --> 07:46.716
we happen to live with.

08:08.780 --> 08:10.490
Thanks, Dewey!

