It's Bernard.

08:43.606 --> 08:44.565
Let me see him.

08:44.607 --> 08:45.733
You can't have him.

08:45.775 --> 08:47.777
That's all right,

08:45.775 --> 08:47.777
I can wait.

08:47.819 --> 08:50.364
Next week is

08:47.819 --> 08:50.364
