09:20.227 --> 09:22.312
Do you want to be grounded

09:20.227 --> 09:22.312
like your brothers?

09:22.354 --> 09:24.605
No.

09:26.358 --> 09:29.110
Man, I've never seen Lavernia

09:26.358 --> 09:29.110
