09:35.658 --> 09:38.453
You know Big Don

09:35.658 --> 09:38.453
from accounting?

09:38.495 --> 09:39.620
The guy with one ear?

09:39.662 --> 09:41.248
Yeah. He was going to the privy,

09:41.289 --> 09:43.666
and she dropped on him

09:41.289 --> 09:43.666
just like a spider.

09:43.708 --> 09:45.419
What is wrong with her?!

09:45.460 --> 09:47.546
We were just having

09:45.460 --> 09:47.546
a stupid little argument.

09:47.587 --> 09:49.506
How did it suddenly

09:47.587 --> 09:49.506
turn into a fight?

09:49.548 --> 09:51.007
That's how we

09:49.548 --> 09:51.007
settle things up there.

09:51.049 --> 09:53.301
There are three other fights

09:51.049 --> 09:53.301
scheduled for tomorrow.

09:53.343 --> 09:54.635
Four.

09:54.677 --> 09:57.514
Ned cut in front of Daryl

09:54.677 --> 09:57.514
at the mess line.

09:57.556 --> 09:58.639
Well, I hate

09:57.556 --> 09:58.639
to disappoint you guys,

09:58.681 --> 10:00.308
but I'm not fighting Lavernia.

10:00.350 --> 10:01.809
Really?

10:01.851 --> 10:03.061
Are you sure?

10:03.103 --> 10:05.230
No, no, he'll fight her.

10:05.272 --> 10:06.856
No, I won't.

10:06.898 --> 10:08.608
Thank you!

10:09.484 --> 10:10.651
Hey, fellas, looks like

10:10.693 --> 10:12.653
we're going to have us

10:10.693 --> 10:12.653
