10:12.695 --> 10:13.738
(men cheering)

10:13.780 --> 10:14.822
I'll get the dogs ready.

10:14.864 --> 10:16.450
I'll sharpen

10:14.864 --> 10:16.450
the pig-sticker.

10:16.491 --> 10:18.535
Wait-wait-wait.

10:16.491 --> 10:18.535
What are you talking about?

10:18.577 --> 10:21.246
Look, fighting's the only

10:18.577 --> 10:21.246
entertainment we get up here.

10:21.288 --> 10:22.663
You've seen our TV reception.

10:22.705 --> 10:25.542
So if somebody cheats

10:22.705 --> 10:25.542
the boys out of a fight,

10:25.584 --> 10:27.544
they have a

10:25.584 --> 10:27.544
coward's cotillion.

10:27.586 --> 10:29.670
What the hell

10:27.586 --> 10:29.670
is a coward's cotillion?!

10:29.712 --> 10:31.672
Oh, it's always

10:29.712 --> 10:31.672
a little different.

10:31.714 --> 10:33.467
You never know

10:31.714 --> 10:33.467
what kind of animal

10:33.508 --> 10:35.135
the blood's going to attract.

10:35.176 --> 10:37.596
So my choices are,

10:35.176 --> 10:37.596
I have to fight a woman

10:37.637 --> 10:39.680
or do this stupid

10:37.637 --> 10:39.680
cotillion thing?

10:39.722 --> 10:40.765
Well...

10:40.807 --> 10:45.645
there's always

10:40.807 --> 10:45.645
the howdy stranger.

10:50.191 --> 10:52.402
(squeaking)

11:11.004 --> 11:12.880
How can they make us

11:11.004 --> 11:12.880
wait another 24 hours?

11:12.922 --> 11:15.383
Apparently they're

11:12.922 --> 11:15.383
shorthanded at the lab.

11:15.425 --> 11:18.136
Don't they realize

11:15.425 --> 11:18.136
this is someone's life?

11:23.766 --> 11:24.892
Don't worry, Bernard.

11:24.934 --> 11:26.603
This is for the best.

11:26.645 --> 11:27.728
I'm setting you free.

11:27.770 --> 11:28.938
You won't have to worry

11:28.980 --> 11:31.358
