You have accomplished plenty.

17:03.898 --> 17:06.066
Oh, my God.

17:06.108 --> 17:07.735
You're coming on to me.

17:07.777 --> 17:08.987
What?

17:09.028 --> 17:10.154
Well, you better

17:09.028 --> 17:10.154
peddle your sugar

17:10.196 --> 17:12.657
to somebody else, 'cause

17:10.196 --> 17:12.657
